description: 40 years since The Smiths self-titled debut album. The very best tracks from The Smiths including There Is A Light That Never Goes Out, Back To The Old House, This Night Has Opened My Eyes, Heaven Knows I'm Miserable Now,  This Charming Man and much more.
name: The Smiths: Best
